data.message: Reviewed 14 external designs with honest critique, synthesized patterns, extracted 7 key learnings for future creative work: Identified gap between concept-work (6.5-7.5) and product-work (8-8.5). Key insights: one clever detail > decoration, confidence = restraint, warm palettes differentiate, typography as structure, solve problems not aesthetics.
